                        </div>
                        <div style="text-align: right;">
                          <div style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: 900; color: #ff6600; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 1;">RIXI<span style="color: #1f2937;">LAB</span></div>
                          <p style="margin: 5px 0 0 0; font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280;">rixilab.com • info@rixilab.com</p>
